Usage: getGenerateViaMode [-help] [-auto] [-ndr_only] [-quiet] [-nonDefault]

-help                          # Prints out the command usage
-auto                          # enable auto via generation when design is
                               # loaded (bool, default=false)
-ndr_only                      # generate vias for non default rules only
                               # (bool, default=false)
-quiet                         # Displays the current settings in Tcl list format only
-nonDefault                    # Displays the current settings which are not default settings